<mxCell id="c42" value="Note: This is a strategy discussion map, not an application inventory or architecture roadmap. Vertical position shows visibility in the value chain; horizontal position shows assumed evolution. Lines are value-chain dependencies, not API direction, event flow, process sequence, data movement or implementation timing. To keep the map readable, only primary dependencies are drawn; the screening, fraud, data-access and event components all also rely on the platform utilities (compute, storage, network). Component positions are assumptions for discussion and should be challenged. They are illustrative, not factual assessments of a real bank." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFF8DC;strokeColor=#8A6D3B;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="60" y="850" width="800" height="90" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
